---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="AWS Modernization"
  descripcion="Migrate and modernize your AWS workloads with a structured, zero-downtime approach. Terraform-driven account strategy, ECS/EKS migration paths, and cost-optimized architecture."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section
    style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A2540 0%, #0d2f50 100%); padding: 100px 24px 80px;"
  >
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8"
        style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.15); color: #60A5FA; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.25);"
      >
        Solution · AWS Modernization
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        Modernize your AWS workloads<br />without disrupting production.
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-lg sm:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10"
        style="color: rgba(148,163,184,0.9);"
      >
        Structured migration from legacy infrastructure to modern AWS
        architectures — Terraform-first, zero-downtime, with measurable cost
        reduction from day one.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:-translate-y-px"
          style="background: #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(30,111,255,0.4);"
        >
          Start your modernization
          <svg
            class="w-4 h-4"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
            ><path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg
          >
        </a>
        <a
          href="/projects"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-all hover:bg-white/10"
          style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);"
        >
          View case studies
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key points -->
  <section style="background: #F8FAFC; padding: 80px 24px;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #0A2540;">
          What AWS modernization delivers
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: #64748B;">
          A repeatable path from monolithic, manually-managed infrastructure to
          automated, auditable AWS environments.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {
          [
            {
              title: 'Infrastructure as Code from day one',
              desc: 'Every AWS resource defined in Terraform — VPCs, IAM, ECS/EKS clusters, RDS, and security groups. No manual console work. Full audit trail, reproducible across environments.',
              icon: 'M17.25 6.75L22.5 12l-5.25 5.25m-10.5 0L1.5 12l5.25-5.25m7.5-3l-4.5 16.5',
            },
            {
              title: 'Zero-downtime migration paths',
              desc: 'Blue/green deployments, gradual traffic shifting with ALB weighted routing, and database migration with minimal replica lag. Production continuity is non-negotiable.',
              icon: 'M16.023 9.348h4.992v-.001M2.985 19.644v-4.992m0 0h4.992m-4.993 0l3.181 3.183a8.25 8.25 0 0013.803-3.7M4.031 9.865a8.25 8.25 0 0113.803-3.7l3.181 3.182m0-4.991v4.99',
            },
            {
              title: 'Right-sized compute & cost optimization',
              desc: 'Graviton instance selection, Savings Plans analysis, and reserved capacity planning. Average 30–45% infrastructure cost reduction after the first 90 days.',
              icon: 'M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z',
            },
            {
              title: 'Security & compliance by default',
              desc: 'GuardDuty, Security Hub, SCPs, and VPC flow logs wired from the start. Compliance frameworks (SOC2, PCI-DSS, HIPAA) addressed at the architecture level, not retrofitted.',
              icon: 'M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z',
            },
          ].map(({ title, desc, icon }) => (
            <div
              class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7"
              style="border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06); box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(15,23,42,0.04);"
            >
              <div
                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5"
                style="background: #EEF4FF;"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  style="color: #1E6FFF;"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="1.5"
                    d={icon}
                  />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color: #0A2540;">
                {title}
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748B;">
                {desc}
              </p>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background: #0A2540; padding: 80px 24px;">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        Ready to modernize your AWS infrastructure?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-10" style="color: rgba(148,163,184,0.85);">
        Schedule a 30-minute architecture review. We'll assess your current
        state and outline a concrete modernization path.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:-translate-y-px"
        style="background: #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(30,111,255,0.45);"
      >
        Schedule architecture review
        <svg
          class="w-4 h-4"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
          ><path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg
        >
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- See it in practice -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8" style="border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-left: 4px solid #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(15,23,42,0.04), 0 4px 16px rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
          <div>
            <span class="section-label">See it in practice</span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-3" style="color: #0A2540;">aws-terraform-devops — Production AWS with Terraform</h2>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-semibold flex-shrink-0 ml-4" style="background: #F0FDF4; color: #15803D; border: 1px solid #BBF7D0;">Production</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5" style="color: #64748B;">Modular Terraform stack deploying Flask on EKS with RDS PostgreSQL 15 Multi-AZ, dual GitHub Actions and Jenkins pipelines, and SonarCloud coverage gates. Every module independently versioned and reusable.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-5">
          {['Terraform','EKS','RDS PostgreSQL 15','GitHub Actions','Jenkins','SonarCloud','Flask','Docker'].map(t => (
            <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-medium" style="background: #F1F5F9; color: #475569;">{t}</span>
          ))}
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <a href="/projects/aws-terraform-devops" class="text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg" style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF;">Read case study →</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/lra-cloud-ops/aws-terraform-devops" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg" style="background: #F1F5F9; color: #0A2540;">GitHub →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
